---
title: Chorizo Sausage and Onion Skewers with Bravas Wedges and Toasted Almond Topped Sticky Veg
description: If there's one thing that makes us happy, it's seeing families cooking together in the kitchen! This is a great one to get kids involved in … especially threading the chorizo and veggie chunks onto the skewers, which is pretty fun (but pretty messy!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-sausage-skewers-2e544330-25f95c94.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chorizo-sausage-skewers-5ef37f17c584c74e092aeef2-8a37f31a.pdf
